Interface NewItemListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EditCaseInfoComponent, EditDiagnosisComponent

    public interface NewItemListener
    The observer pattern is used. A class can implement this interface if the class needs information about: a new item should be added or an existing item should be edited.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Group White, I2p, BFH Berne, Contact
